(44, 2, 11, 19, 26, 7, 7, NULL, 'Connection of Wondrous Works', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of proclaiming God''s wondrous works. Acts 2:11 mentions speaking of ''the wonderful works of God,'' while Psalms 26:7 expresses a desire to ''tell of all thy wondrous works.'' This connection highlights the importance of sharing God''s deeds.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
